cc:Work.dc:title: Full size wood wheelbarrow plan
cc:Work.dc:description: This is a project I did with the children; from used pressure treated fence boards. The handles are made from decking boards, carefully selected to have less knots. Deck boards are stronger than fence boards, but much heavier. I had the old steel wheel for years; if it didn't fit, I would have made a wooden wheel from two layers of wood pieces at right angles.
